documentType: FBI rap sheet / criminal history record
summary: This is an FBI rap sheet response from the New York State Division of Criminal Justice Services to an FBI inquiry. It contains standard criminal history record caveats and indicates the subject's DNA is not in CODIS but should be collected. No specific criminal history entries or fingerprint/images are transmitted in this portion.

keyFacts: The document is an official FBI rap sheet/criminal history record response dated October 6, 2021.
It states that all entries are based on fingerprint comparisons and pertain to the same individual.
It contains a DNA indicator noting 'DNA NOT IN CODIS - COLLECT DNA'.
The record is provided for official use only and regulated by law.
No specific criminal history entries, fingerprint images, or photo images are transmitted in this portion of the record.
